Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.62,0:00:11.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.82,0:00:18.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Shimofuri
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.71,0:00:19.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.77,0:00:23.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.45,0:00:24.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is Shirofumi's first time, nice to meet you
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the declining-in-popularity-Shimofumi?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, Matsumoto
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell? \N  Matsumoto, where did you hear this?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.06,0:00:32.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Never heard of it.\N  -Seems wrong
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.41,0:00:34.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're on the rise.\N  -We're still on the rise
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.86,0:00:35.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was wrong
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're just getting started!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stop this, Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this time
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.99,0:00:44.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are horror-oriented pranks
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Among these, Hamada's favorite is
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.26,0:00:50.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The "Somebody Series"
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh interesting
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.60,0:00:53.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I heard that Hamada enjoys this the most
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.46,0:00:54.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really likes it!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He watches it with his whole mouth open
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.53,0:00:59.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That wide?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.05,0:01:03.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Previously, it was said that the most frightening thing is to open the door and find someone
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.11,0:01:04.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.46,0:01:07.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Someone in the back seat of the car"
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.15,0:01:09.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Wake up and find someone"
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And others like "someone's in the bed"
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.24,0:01:14.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every time Hamada smiles very happily
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there should be none left
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.60,0:01:17.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.49,0:01:21.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, the "Someone Series" is twisted slightly
Dialogue: 2,0:01:21.33,0:01:24.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It will be used to validate a relatively novel theory
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.83,0:01:30.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if a foreigner has lived in Japan for a long time, the first words that come out of their mouth when they are surprised will be their native language
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.16,0:01:31.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They'll react
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A slightly different scenario
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"GOD DAMN" or something like that?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"GOD DAMN" and the like
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, just leave
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Takada really made us nervous too
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.74,0:01:49.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This volume is the that of the ring announcer
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.39,0:01:49.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.28,0:01:54.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shortly, a verification involving foreigners
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.33,0:01:56.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.61,0:02:00.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How long with Rossy go along with suspicious things?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Little girl selling matches?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.37,0:02:07.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Men with scary faces have been told "I won't give you my daughter"
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.40,0:02:31.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if a foreigner has lived in Japan for a long time, the first words that come out of their mouth when they are surprised will be their native language
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.91,0:02:37.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this time, we are testing foreign people who are active in Japan
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With an approach that has a 100% rate of scaring people
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The dependable "Someone Series"
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The initial target is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1184.5,250)}Girolamo has been here for 32 years?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.47,0:02:57.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the setting is
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.78,0:03:02.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A locker room in the lounge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Japanese still isn't great
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's this guy every time
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I Love you baby
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I Love you…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.07,0:03:16.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,@%#$!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems like he said something
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.91,0:03:19.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I Love you…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,@%#$!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Asshole, what the hell!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The second sentence is "asshole" but
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.23,0:03:38.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first sentence sounds like Italian
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What exactly did he say?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.60,0:03:45.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a strange man here, a stalker
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.88,0:03:48.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We confirmed
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a particularly... particularly strange person in...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was a shock!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did you say when you saw this male?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's "die!"
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah... Japanese...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not his native language
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.13,0:04:13.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will it change back to speak Italian when you are scared?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You usually speak Japanese. \N -But... but...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really like "die!"
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From time to time, i'll say it
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.71,0:04:28.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What should you have said in Italian at this time?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.01,0:04:32.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mamma Mia would be better, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.72,0:04:37.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But, for me, the usage of "die!" is the same
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Die!!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Asshole, what the hell!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why "die!"?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.25,0:04:46.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the next target is
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who would say "die!"?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wrong way to use it, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In Japan for 23 years: Caiya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Caiya is really scary
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.45,0:04:58.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The setting is "someone is in the back seat of the car"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Might get hit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really could be hit in the chaos of the situation
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,While a fictitious interview was in progress
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.73,0:05:07.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person is placed on standby in the back seat of the private car she drove in
Dialogue: 2,0:05:07.64,0:05:10.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Preparations complete
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After this
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.20,0:05:19.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Caiya, who was talking to someone while returning to the car
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.81,0:05:19.03,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1220,250)}Definitely not in a happy phone conversation
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true, a lot has happened
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to on the phone?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.07,0:05:27.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already in English
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If she is scared like this
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There should be a sound like "Oh my God"
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What'll happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK  see you soon  bye
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.67,0:06:02.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A simple reaction
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And due to too much fear
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She escaped from the car with full force
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.05,0:06:13.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we revealed the truth
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.25,0:06:20.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm not thinking straight right now
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seeing someone in the car
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.23,0:06:24.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is already trauma, trauma!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.16,0:06:29.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, I'm scared to death, oh my god
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.90,0:06:35.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When calming down, she spoke English from time to time
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.38,0:06:40.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the first reaction was a horror movie-like scream
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target is
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.62,0:06:52.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In Japan for 13 years, Nwala
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.47,0:07:01.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, he was set up to sleep in a hotel and "wake up to find someone"
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We first confirm he's asleep
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.15,0:07:14.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before an older man enters
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy is awesome!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is so scary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, this is so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This would definitely be scary
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.16,0:07:30.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next thing to do before he wakes up naturally is just to wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This job is also not easy
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.77,0:07:36.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then after two hours
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:54.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a normal reaction
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.09,0:08:17.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scared that he fell out of bed, but the first sentence was in Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scared the hell out of me!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No English at all
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, really
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Authentic Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely won't sleep tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How could you do this? Seriously
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep. He's still here!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have to get up at four o'clock to go to "Good Morning Studio"
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This program is live!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Angry
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.24,0:08:56.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And I locked the door
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How could you still come in?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a master key is?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Master Key
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of timing is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target is
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.76,0:09:16.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In Japan for 33 years: Dave Spector
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.22,0:09:21.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time it was in Dave's dedicated cloakroom
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.05,0:09:25.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where the man with a high success rate is lurking
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we start immediately
