Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Completely in Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Who?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scared the hell out of me
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.65,0:10:09.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really "oh my godou!" this one
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.98,0:10:13.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He even says "oh my god" in Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.93,0:10:17.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,33 years of living in Japan were not in vain
Dialogue: 2,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really "oh my godou!" this one
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not even here
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last target is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really want to here them speak English
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.16,0:10:35.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,21 years in Japan: Bobby Ologun
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.77,0:10:37.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bobby is also very timid
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.93,0:10:40.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The set up is "someone in the bed" trick
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we let the family go out first
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.38,0:10:49.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A verification of an isolated single person in his own house
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.89,0:11:00.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When he gets home, he first performs the daily task of checking stock prices
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now he's ready for bed
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.00,0:11:27.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably he doesn't notice there's someone next to him
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.09,0:11:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will he sleep with an older man he doesn't know for a whole night?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.42,0:11:45.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bobby didn't notice the man hiding under the blanket and went to sleep
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell--
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell--
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.68,0:12:15.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bobby who felt a sense of dissonance from his back when he turned over
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell--
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first sentence was clearly in Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Immediately after
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.20,0:12:41.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He fell into a state of panic with the dramatic effect of frantically pressing the wrong switch
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.95,0:12:43.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who!?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.17,0:12:49.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts...it hurts...it hurts
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.98,0:12:53.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He knocks down the sliding door in one move
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:05.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Crying crying crying
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Someone has died
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know anything
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep in the bed?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I got in
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you not pay attention at all at that time?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was sleeping on my side the whole time
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.58,0:13:29.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you say when you are frightened in Nigerian?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.80,0:13:40.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0201FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\c\3c}Japanese pranks will always end in Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The result turned out to be this
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes\N  -No native language spoken
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.95,0:13:49.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is too much, not good for the heart
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary to watch
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.02,0:13:50.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But, how to put it?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.90,0:13:54.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They'll calm down eventually
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.94,0:13:56.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then they'll speak their native language
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.40,0:14:00.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at the time they won't
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.25,0:14:05.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They must be dreaming in Japanese, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stayed too long, have become completely Japanese
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.35,0:14:13.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are there such people? Only dreaming in the native language
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.00,0:14:17.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you live too long, your dreams become Japanese, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.43,0:14:23.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want it to keep going like this until Bobby speaks his native language
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Poor thing \N -Its enough for him to hit the door
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The doors of their house will be all gone
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Incredible, the energy
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lights in the living room also flickered as if they were about to break
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lights and doors are running out
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The light is the same as lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:44.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Savannah's Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:59.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, I bring a project about the world's most innocent and gentle man
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:06.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is literally the most innocent and gentle man in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:12.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy's acceptance of everything has gone so far that its scary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:18.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You must all know Rossy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:22.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is really gentle, innocent, and tolerant of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:25.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Totally non-angry, non-doubting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:29.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A man who feels nothing is out of place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:35.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember the "Strange Man Contest" project that was conducted for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:41.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In a project such as, persuading a child to continue to be a shut-in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:45.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the way, he suddenly became furious with the mother of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:49.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Loudly scolded the mother "how can you do this to your child"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is also a reflection of his gentle caring nature
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:56.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The ending was that Rossy became shut in the room and couldn't get out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even at that inexplicable point, he accepted it without question
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's really an incredible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That part was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:06.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We did all kinds of tricks on this gentle Rossy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To what extent will he accept them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:17.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy's acceptance of everything has gone so far that its scary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:26.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we first asked the person who knows Rossy best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His wife
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:32.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy's acceptance of everything has gone so far that its scary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He tolerates everything, basically
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:40.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it will be incredible for everyone to witness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really feel like that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you encountered any strange things lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:49.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example, the entrance to a convenience store
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:54.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The ruler they measure the approximate height of a thief
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:54.59,note_Wed - 复制,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※It is also available at financial institutions, amusement parks, etc. It is used for witnesses to recall the approximate height of the possible culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy he...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:01.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He thought it was normal to measure his own height and happily did so
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And also
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:05.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He has very bad eyesight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't wear contact lenses, he is completely blind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sometimes he will forget to take off his contact lenses and go to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And still put another pair on the next morning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Won't even notice he's wearing double contact lenses
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:23.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we spent several days watching Rossy closely
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy, he is really gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Help with incredibly heavy luggage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feels like it will be very interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happens if he's told, "Please can you take this luggage that cannot be put on the floor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He will always hold it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:42.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They'll say "Don't put it on the floor", right?\N  -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then he won't put it on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we called out Rossy for a fake job
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So at this point
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you take this for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:59.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I forgot something, I need to go back quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, so heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this can not be put on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because inside are very valuable things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I leave for a little bit...for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. \N -No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:13.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, obviously you're so busy. I'm very sorry. I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.03,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It looks so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:25.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As you can see, Rossy calmly agreed to carry a full 20kg box of sand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:28.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no difference with the sand on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We also inexplicably added a requirement that prohibits putting it on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Normally you'd put it on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:41.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So far there is no doubt that the luggage was not put on the ground as agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are not curious about what'd happen if put it on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:46.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:49.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. \N -It's okay, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. It's a big help.\N  -Don't mention it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go around to the back of the area
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because this luggage is very heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does it mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We'll walk a little bit, there might be a place to take a cab
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the pick-up point is close, you might as well take one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let me walk you to the cab
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:12.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kindly helped to carry the sand to the loading point
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:21.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The cab drives to the wrong destination but charges as normal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He wont get angry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When paying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:29.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well...probably will hesitate a few times
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:34.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Um... please send me to TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,TBS？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one in Akasaka. \N -Oh, it's in Akasaka, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok \N -Okay, thanks for the ride
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:47.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The work destination from Shinbashi is Akasaka, about 3km away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:53.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, the cab went to Shinagawa,  the opposite direction of Akasaka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The result?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd surely be angry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Driver, excuse me?\N  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:02.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if we're going in the right direction
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The wording is so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm driving in the direction of Akasaka, TBS, so its fine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I feel like you are driving towards Shinagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you drive towards the centre?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you drive in the direction of the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it will be closer to TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:21.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Relying on the afternoon sun and the position of the sun, the driver was directed to drive west
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's over there, over there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In terms of direction
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No...that...  \N-Hahaha no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:30.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's that way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's not angry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:35.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can get off here and transfer if you don't know the way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please stop for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're heading to Shinagawa now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too gentle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh... I don't think there's anything wrong with that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I don't arrive, it's not good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:55.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy started to get anxious about being late because of his serious personality
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now we are in the direction of TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not the right direction, although I'm taking the liberty of making that judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's my fault
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please let me off here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will get to the destination in some other way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I get out of the car now, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't say this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just drop me off here. It's close to Shinagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here, a little to the side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Wait a minute. \N -We've already passed Shinagawa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can you let me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:24.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Driver, you've already driven past Shinagawa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:25.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this the direction of Akasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, Akasaka is in the opposite direction
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong, Mr. Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:32.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, this time the driver is determined not to let him off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this setup?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:34.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:37.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I may have to do something not so good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:40.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I may contact the police
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't let me out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:47.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You may be held criminally liable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hearing these 3 numbers the program team immediately softened
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:53.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we stopped here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I made such an arbitrary request
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Arbitrary request?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:01.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, the fare is 2010 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:07.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite being pulled further away from his destination
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:11.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is nonetheless thankful and paid the fair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm really sorry. \N -It's okay, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:16.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making arbitrary demands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:18.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry about making arbitrary demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:38.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Day 2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:45.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\frx270\t(0,170,\frx360)\org(712.5,840)}{\3c&H1515D0&}Verification ③ {\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\c&H000000&}{\pos(714,880)}Stranger asks to borrow his cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:42.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A request from a complete stranger to "borrow a cell phone"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:42.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd surely want to refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:45.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He rightfully lends it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:48.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:49.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hung up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is your unlock code?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:54.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unlock code? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:58.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there an unlock code?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I call again? \N -Yes, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:01.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doesn't even know of the existence of the unlock code and the phone doesn't have a lock screen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:08.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about personal privacy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:10.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3rd Day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cookie asks him to look after his son for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If strongly requested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:21.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably would agree
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:25.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,During a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:29.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A staff member leaves momentarily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where do you live? Have you moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is the room very spacious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, the room is not very spacious. 2LDK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:40.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have two children?\N  -2, 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:43.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can the toys be packed up to make room?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:46.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm?\N  -Can you make room by packing up their toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:49.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Toys can be packed to make room for almost one person's space
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:51.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can it sleep two children?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:53.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Two children?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:56.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah probably
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:24:01.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My wife always had a dream to study language abroad
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I don't have time to take care of children
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:07.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh-?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.26,0:24:08.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the time is confirmed can you please
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:13.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Take care of my child for about 3 months
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:16.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is not something that can't be done
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of a variety of reasons its not impossible, not impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:21.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But for example, going to school
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.34,0:24:23.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And stuff like that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:25.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Taking them there and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't mean transferring them my child's school
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.45,0:24:30.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I mean parents and such
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.71,0:24:35.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are still many things that need to be adapted
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.92,0:24:38.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If its stable then its fine
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.76,0:24:43.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the child is not given a happy experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.13,0:24:44.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If they just suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.20,0:24:47.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you can't take care of them?\N  -I'm not saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.87,0:24:49.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it is not impossible to take care of, but I can not go to your home to take care of them
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.07,0:24:52.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But since you entrusted me with the care of a life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.81,0:24:57.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy, who is very sensitive about human life and children's matters
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.25,0:25:00.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly and carefully thought out and answered carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:02.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well you can look at it as just an extended sleepover
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.18,0:25:03.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, 3 months is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.91,0:25:06.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3 months is a bit... uh
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.38,0:25:10.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably because someone else's kid is staying here
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.22,0:25:14.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd feel a sense of responsibility, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.26,0:25:18.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't say yes so easily
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.33,0:25:20.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the mood is "ah yeah fine"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.66,0:25:23.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's just like borrowing something
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.67,0:25:26.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Then you can borrow it next time" or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.34,0:25:29.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3 months is a bit...  \N-I don't understand you, for example
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.97,0:25:33.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3 months is a bit too long
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.14,0:25:35.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,1 week and 2 weeks is quite manageable
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.31,0:25:37.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then help me look after them for two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:38.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.75,0:25:40.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2 weeks is perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.05,0:25:42.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But 3 months is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.02,0:25:46.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You take care of them for 2 weeks and then I pick them up for a day and then give you them back for another two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.12,0:25:49.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can be up to 3 months repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.13,0:25:51.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.27,0:25:52.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why does he look accepting of the length all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.40,0:25:54.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah... yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.66,0:25:58.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is successfully convinced thanks to Cookie's sophisticated argument
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.56,0:26:01.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Slowly ground into agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:06.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is really gentle with children, no matter what children
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.14,0:26:12.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We added something for Rossy, who is very gentle with children
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.28,0:26:15.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then I will contact you when I have the chance.\N  -Ok thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.29,0:26:17.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:23.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Big brother. \N -Scared the hell out of me, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.39,0:26:26.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you want to buy some matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.96,0:26:29.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The little girl who sells matches
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.57,0:26:32.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\frx270\t(0,170,\frx360)\org(712.5,840)}{\3c&H1515D0&}Verification ⑤ {\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\c&H000000&}{\pos(714,880)}The little girl who sells matches in 2019
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:32.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please. \N -No, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.24,0:26:33.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:36.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much, how much, how much, how much, how much, what to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.34,0:26:38.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much? What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.51,0:26:39.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can buy one
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.68,0:26:44.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, then 1000 yen, please
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.25,0:26:45.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A little expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.45,0:26:49.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just buy one, one
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.72,0:26:52.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here, here's your money. Give me the matches. \N -Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.76,0:26:54.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Go for it! \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.96,0:26:57.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.45,0:27:01.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although a high price
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.29,0:27:04.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He still accepted the scene with equanimity
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.05,0:27:06.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Normally you'd be looking for a camera here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.80,0:27:09.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The unreasonableness of the tests slowly escalate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.97,0:27:12.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,4th Day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.64,0:27:15.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H050510&\b0}Abandoned dogs on the roadside
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.79,0:27:19.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However this dog is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:19.35,special_Wed_3_X,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,610)}Please be kind enough to take her in, she's a little bitch named Mocha
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.69,0:27:25.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,AIBO？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.42,0:27:29.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,AIBO might be adopted by him
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.59,0:27:31.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about that either
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.13,0:27:33.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would he be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.86,0:27:35.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,May say "what is this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.90,0:27:51.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As you can see, after a short glance, he walks past
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.56,0:27:52.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.75,0:27:56.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Immediately after this, he sent his wife this LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:27:59.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you want AIBO?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.66,0:28:06.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you do at XX elementary school there's one, we could take it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:10.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,AIBO? AIBO is the robot dog! Haha
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.28,0:28:18.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's an abandoned AIBO dog in a box named Mocha
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.30,0:28:20.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It says "AIBO"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.21,0:28:24.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The kids will probably like it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.12,0:28:27.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of rushing to work
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.38,0:28:29.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although not personally taking it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.86,0:28:36.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As the abandoned dog is an electronic dog his feelings are less strong
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.41,0:28:41.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next was a verification as part of a fake health program
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.81,0:28:43.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Firstly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.43,0:28:46.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.74,0:28:51.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The micro-mic has changed to coin operated
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.07,0:28:54.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Coin-operated?  \N-Yes, coin-operated...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.44,0:29:00.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\frx270\t(0,170,\frx360)\org(712.5,840)}{\3c&H1515D0&}Verification ⑦ {\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\c&H000000&}{\pos(714,880)}If you don't use a 100-yen coin the microphone wont work
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.09,0:29:00.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.47,0:29:04.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy-san, could you please put in 100 yen first...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.09,0:29:06.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I know, I know, I'll get the money. \N -You have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.42,0:29:08.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll go and look
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.29,0:29:10.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Should have change, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.11,0:29:14.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His acceptance has reached ridiculous heights
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.80,0:29:19.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How long does it last?\N  -How long does it last?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.17,0:29:21.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,100 yen will last about an hour. \N -That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:24.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The more words you say, the faster the battery drops
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.01,0:29:26.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Haha new type of microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.41,0:29:27.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.57,0:29:29.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No suspicion at all
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.22,0:29:36.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally Rossy's over-acceptance is at the point of being frightening
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.82,0:29:40.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regardless, he puts on the micro-mic with 100 yen invested first
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.85,0:29:44.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, the physical strength test
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.41,0:29:46.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.45,0:29:48.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ready ~ Start
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.05,0:29:56.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The sound of 100 yen completely affects the important sound recording of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.61,0:29:58.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Putting the cart before the horse
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.18,0:30:00.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,End
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.41,0:30:01.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,56th
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.41,0:30:02.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are so many?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.65,0:30:03.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.93,0:30:08.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, Rossy did not care about this at all
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.69,0:30:10.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So tired \N -Well done
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.95,0:30:11.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the compliment
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.51,0:30:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After this also
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.67,0:30:16.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Round trip running
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.79,0:30:20.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Above average
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.28,0:30:27.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Accompanied by the sound of the mic he completes the seven physical tests
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.65,0:30:32.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the health diagnosis
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.41,0:30:34.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, without further ado
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.85,0:30:36.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's have a health check
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.11,0:30:37.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, please
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.11,0:30:40.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So please strip down to your underwear
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.82,0:30:41.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, understood
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.82,0:30:45.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then put your clothes in this basket
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.90,0:30:49.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As you can see, Rossy took off his shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.29,0:30:50.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now lets start the vision check
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.89,0:30:53.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please look at the table over there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.80,0:30:58.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\frx270\t(0,170,\frx360)\org(712.5,840)}{\3c&H1515D0&}Verification ⑧ {\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\c&H000000&}{\pos(714,880)}Stripping isn't necessary for the tests
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.38,0:30:58.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please stand in the white line
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.80,0:30:59.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.64,0:31:03.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Ah, its a little hard to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.21,0:31:05.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To the left, ah, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.88,0:31:10.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, these tests that had nothing to do with nudity
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.99,0:31:15.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, he gets dressed and goes to receive the results
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.55,0:31:20.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The x-ray image is done\N  -Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:23.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look. \N -Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.09,0:31:25.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you see this part?\N  -No
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:31.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have a seed sprouting in your stomach.  \N-No, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:42.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\frx270\t(0,170,\frx360)\org(712.5,840)}{\3c&H1515D0&}Verification ⑨ {\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\c&H000000&}{\pos(714,880)}Watermelon seed germinating in stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.47,0:31:36.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I presume its a watermelon seed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.74,0:31:39.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've been... \N -I've been eating watermelon lately
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.54,0:31:40.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you swallow seeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.84,0:31:42.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah that's really watermelon seeds
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:44.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, two days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.85,0:31:52.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Karateka Yabetaro asked Rossy to eat some watermelon
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.96,0:31:54.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, i'll be careful in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.99,0:31:58.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take all the seeds out in future
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.60,0:31:59.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's very rare
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.90,0:32:02.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm also worried about Yabe, I ate it with him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.05,0:32:04.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is still worried about others
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.30,0:32:07.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Watermelon seeds sprouted in the x-ray image
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.37,0:32:09.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think he'll believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:15.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He still quite likes this kind of fantasy things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.11,0:32:17.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has there been anything before? Something fantastical?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.48,0:32:20.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fantasy - well - for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.38,0:32:22.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a knife skill called "Chikiri" that cuts cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.62,0:32:26.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He felt that a more superior knife technique, "Ten Thousand Cuts", also existed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:33.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another example is the Romance Car, which he thought was a train for the elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:33.56,note_Wed - 复制,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Romance Car: The term "Romance Car" was originally used to refer to a train with a Romance Seat, i.e., a couple's seat in a group of 2. In 1991, Odakyu Electric Railway registered the term as its own trademark, so it now refers specifically to the special trains operated by Odakyu Electric Railway
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.83,0:32:36.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's sprouting
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.27,0:32:38.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like a bean sprout. Will it grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.94,0:32:42.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If there is enough nutrition in the stomach, it may grow
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.27,0:32:43.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it was the first time I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.97,0:32:48.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will not be a problem if left unattended
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.41,0:32:50.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But what if?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.68,0:32:55.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it grows into a watermelon fruit in the stomach, it's a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.81,0:32:57.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is really amazing, if it'll grow into a watermelon
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.52,0:33:01.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is medicine to make this bud wilt. I'll bring it to you now
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.99,0:33:05.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This bottle is the medicine that makes the buds wilt
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.23,0:33:08.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This bottle is the medicine that will destroy it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.43,0:33:10.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please pay attention to the order of taking the medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.70,0:33:14.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't germinate and drink this bottle of blight medicine, your stomach will be perforated
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.54,0:33:19.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.18,0:33:21.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, there is one last thing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.85,0:33:27.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last verification is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.28,0:33:29.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is our first meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.39,0:33:30.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm the new AD Shino
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.92,0:33:32.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, the same last name
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.56,0:33:33.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? \N -My name is Shino too
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.66,0:33:34.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.36,0:33:36.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, my name is also Shino...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.23,0:33:37.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.43,0:33:41.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The city and vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.77,0:33:42.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yasei?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.64,0:33:43.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, Yasei
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.53,0:33:46.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I would say the "word" town with "wild" in Nogahara
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.64,0:33:49.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Same word, same word, right? \N -The same word!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.91,0:34:01.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\frx270\t(0,170,\frx360)\org(712.5,840)}{\3c&H1515D0&}Verification⑩ {\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\c&H000000&}{\pos(714,880)}Received a request from AD to borrow money
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.38,0:33:56.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fake AD has been present all day
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.77,0:34:01.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He puts forward a request for money
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.93,0:34:07.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will Rossy lend money to someone he has just met and has no relationship with?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.16,0:34:11.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.59,0:34:12.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I need 3 million
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.60,0:34:14.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a little tough, and I don't have that much money
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.53,0:34:16.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3 million, I can't get it by tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.37,0:34:18.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tell me your contact information
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.47,0:34:23.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if its possible
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.38,0:34:28.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you give up because of this it'll be difficult for you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.41,0:34:34.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although he could not immediately come up with the loan because of his own financial problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.14,0:34:41.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy nonetheless listened gently and carefully to the AD troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.96,0:34:44.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.33,0:34:46.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We have to work together
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.97,0:34:51.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And for some reason he makes the promise to "work together"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.93,0:34:49.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.15,0:35:00.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, we move to ask him about the strange events over the past few days
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.94,0:35:05.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we got him in under the guise of a fake program
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.08,0:35:10.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you encountered anything unusual lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.99,0:35:13.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently? Is there a limit to what kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.46,0:35:19.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you encounter any strange or unbelievable things in your daily life?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.04,0:35:19.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.00,0:35:25.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The year number changed, something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.20,0:35:27.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see.  \N-Different from the past
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.19,0:35:26.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Say the watermelon thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.10,0:35:28.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Within the last week
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.54,0:35:32.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something unusual, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.31,0:35:35.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The weather is colder than expected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.68,0:35:38.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I recently went to the dentist
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.65,0:35:44.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now I have dentures and need to get a new tooth or something
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.80,0:35:47.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not about those things
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.82,0:35:52.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just 30 minutes ago things like this happened
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.83,0:35:54.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Completely ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.00,0:36:00.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As we fear he will be unable to realize it himself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.00,0:36:03.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is actually Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.67,0:36:05.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh-
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.71,0:36:07.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.34,0:36:13.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rossy's acceptance of all things is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.45,0:36:15.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.29,0:36:16.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You accepted a lot of strange things
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.39,0:36:21.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no. Is there someone else named Rossy? \N -No, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.10,0:36:25.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0201FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\3c\c}He's really scary
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.59,0:36:29.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.84,0:36:32.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you see the final conclusion?  \N-What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.89,0:36:34.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm a little confused
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.13,0:36:37.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He thinks there are a lot of Rossys, thinks its verifying different Rossys?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.80,0:36:40.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He didn't think anything weird happened to him, did he? \N -That's probably it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.73,0:36:42.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah... I see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.96,0:36:45.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did the other Rossys encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.15,0:36:47.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He himself hasn't encountered anything \N -Thinks he hasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.84,0:36:52.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So other people named Rossy experienced lots of weird things
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.62,0:36:54.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is what he thinks it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.73,0:36:58.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So he thinks that nothing happened to him
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.36,0:37:00.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To Rossy...\N  -He thinks it was all normal
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.85,0:37:03.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are now the closest to Rossy's mindset
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.98,0:37:07.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\N  -Seems like it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.97,0:37:11.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.67,0:37:13.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The driver
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.51,0:37:18.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This part is good, he didn't get angry at all
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.24,0:37:22.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Using Rossy as a comparison
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.00,0:37:25.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I would like to see the Hamada version of this same scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.90,0:37:28.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it were Hamada... \N -I'm sure he would have been furious
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.21,0:37:31.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'd probably kick the kid selling matches
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.36,0:37:40.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is everybody's theories
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.22,0:37:42.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenter is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.44,0:37:47.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tamura Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.65,0:37:53.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory I have brought this time is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.88,0:37:59.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Men with scary faces have been told "I won't give you my daughter"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.94,0:38:02.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Won't give them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.49,0:38:08.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is about people with scary auras meeting parents
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.40,0:38:09.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.14,0:38:13.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If they go to meet the parents, they'll will be told that they won't give their daughter to someone like them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.40,0:38:16.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Matsumoto? You have a daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.24,0:38:19.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Me in the position of parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.16,0:38:21.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If someone with a scary look comes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.61,0:38:25.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well... definitely not if they have swastika on their face
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.52,0:38:29.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not really that far
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.68,0:38:33.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, if the attitude is not good, it'd be impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.02,0:38:34.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did Hamada meet the parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.32,0:38:36.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.81,0:38:39.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened? Did they say, "I won't give you my daughter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.84,0:38:42.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.43,0:38:46.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you go with a fake pinky finger? \N -No pinky?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.04,0:38:49.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's very convincing \N-No pinky?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.26,0:38:52.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You tug it, it won't fall off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.56,0:38:54.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It will come off \N -You tug at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.60,0:38:57.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It will fall off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.67,0:39:01.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My dad is also a strange man
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.28,0:39:03.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I was curious to have them meet
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.28,0:39:05.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.51,0:39:09.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What would your father do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.29,0:39:07.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will be the reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.06,0:39:17.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Men with scary faces have been told "I won't give you my daughter"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.52,0:39:21.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first interview was with this man
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.76,0:39:29.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both arms embroidered with tattoos and huge ear lobes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.04,0:39:33.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His head is also full of tattoos
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.15,0:39:35.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its Bam Bam Bigelow!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.92,0:39:40.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not caring about being poor
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.04,0:39:44.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would someone be fearful that their daughter was going to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:50.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have new tattoos?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.13,0:39:51.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.67,0:39:57.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A large piece
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.74,0:39:59.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it.\N  -That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.88,0:40:02.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a "gout" tattoo. \N -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.45,0:40:05.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It says gout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.55,0:40:08.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You had gout? \N -I had gout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.05,0:40:10.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then got a gout tattoo?\N  -Got the tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.65,0:40:13.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.16,0:40:17.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I drank too much, so I got it to make sure I don't forget I had gout
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.96,0:40:21.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This scary-looking guy is controlling his purine intake
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.27,0:40:25.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you met a girlfriend's parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.17,0:40:27.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Twice
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.10,0:40:28.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Twice? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.54,0:40:29.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.81,0:40:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She told me that "my father is very strict" and "be aware of it"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.98,0:40:37.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I went there and was ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.45,0:40:41.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ignored?\N  -Yes, ignored. Didn't say anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.72,0:40:43.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How did that meeting with the parents end?
