Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.96,0:40:52.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard the words "I won't give you my daughter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.13,0:40:53.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't being ignored the same?
