Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:10.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Neat and tiday
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.68,0:41:15.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the tattoo...  \N-You could see the tattoos still
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.59,0:41:19.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also shaved my beard
