Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.56,0:41:31.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They said "Don't talk to me, get out" and "Get out of my house"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.15,0:41:38.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite the closed door, they had a child and married
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.38,0:41:42.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super opposed to me, still are
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.13,0:41:46.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And this fierce-looking man too
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.78,0:41:50.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is possible that the tattoo wasn't seen as it was covered
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.75,0:41:52.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why is it hated?
