Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.66,0:42:00.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, this is the kind of tattoo that will show even if you wear long sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.50,0:42:04.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The other party said, "Are you kidding me?" "That's ridiculous"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.60,0:42:10.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true that the parents' generation still has a strong aversion to tattoos
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.32,0:42:14.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the midst of all this, this tattooed guy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.51,0:42:17.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Please let me marry your daughter" like this
