Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.02,0:43:02.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Told me "dye your hair black and take out the earrings"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.09,0:43:07.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to do things other people tell me
