Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.62,0:43:36.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was welcomed very warmly and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.39,0:43:39.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After meeting me she also began to wear earrings
