Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.04,0:43:58.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was shocked to be refused
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.65,0:44:04.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And this fierce-looking man sipping whisky on the street
