Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.11,0:44:31.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My mother-in-law doesn't like this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.71,0:44:34.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was told to "take them all off" so I did when we met
